room_title: Escape room "Escape from Kindergarten" by School of Hard Locks in Oceanside
room_description: Did you cry for mommy on your first day of kindergarten? Well unless she is locked inside with you - Mommy can't help you now! Don't be deceived by the surroundings, kindergarten was NEVER this hard! Forget ABCs and 123s - do you remember enough about your colors and shapes to help you unlock the door in 60 minutes or less?
